    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the FEA modeling framework for COU1 based on passing validation metrics across all three QoIs (E/uval < 1.96 for stiffness; <10% error for yield force and force at 40 mm displacement). The shortfall in Test conditions (Gradation 2 achieved vs. Gradation 3 required) was noted but judged acceptable given the standardized nature of ASTM F1717 and the corroborating multi-laboratory experimental evidence. Numerical solver error and Use error factors were considered beyond scope for this submission cycle; the team acknowledged these gaps but did not formally evaluate their impact on overall credibility given the modelRiskLevel of 3.",
